# Events

As per IETF model, everything discussed in physical meetings will be passed through the digital communication channels for the whole community to discuss before it is accepted.

### Berlin September 7 - 9.

The first physical meeting of the Token Ring is planned to coincide with [EthBerlin](https://ethberlin.com/).
